metadata/org.jboss.shrinkwrap/shrinkwrap-api/index.json:9:    "description" : "ShrinkWrap API provides the client-facing interfaces and archive model for creating Java archives such as JAR, WAR, EAR, and resource adapter packages in code. It defines archive, asset, importer, exporter, formatter, container, and class loader abstractions used by ShrinkWrap implementations and tests.",
