metadata/args4j/args4j/index.json:9:    "description" : "args4j is a Java command-line argument parser that maps options and arguments onto annotated fields and methods. It supports type-specific option handlers, usage generation, and localization so applications can define command-line interfaces with less manual parsing code.",
