metadata/org.sangria-graphql/sangria-derivation_3/index.json:9:    "description" : "Sangria Derivation provides Scala macros for deriving Sangria GraphQL object, input object, and enum types from Scala types. It lets Sangria users customize the generated schema with field selection, renaming, documentation, deprecation, tags, complexity, and related derivation settings.",
