metadata/org.sangria-graphql/macro-visit_3/index.json:9:    "description" : "macro-visit is a Scala macro library that generates type-safe visitor code for sealed case-class hierarchies. It supports non-recursive traversal, immutable transformations, skipping or breaking traversal, and visiting supported collection and option fields, making it useful for AST processing.",
