metadata/org.sangria-graphql/sangria-marshalling-api_3/index.json:9:    "description" : "Sangria Marshalling API defines the common marshalling and unmarshalling abstractions used by Sangria GraphQL integrations. It lets JSON or other data-format modules plug into Sangria by converting GraphQL inputs and results to and from Scala values.",
