metadata/org.sangria-graphql/sangria-core_3/index.json:9:    "description" : "Sangria Core is the main Scala GraphQL implementation for defining schemas, validating queries, and executing GraphQL operations. It provides the execution engine, schema model, validation rules, introspection support, rendering utilities, and marshalling hooks used by Sangria-based GraphQL servers and tools.",
