metadata/io.arrow-kt/arrow-annotations-jvm/index.json:9:    "description" : "Arrow Annotations provides Kotlin annotations used by Arrow components, including the @optics annotation for generating optics such as lenses, prisms, optionals, isos, and DSL helpers. The artifact also includes the @synthetic marker annotation used by Arrow tooling to mark generated or synthetic API elements.",
