metadata/org.jboss.arquillian.container/arquillian-container-test-impl-base/index.json:9:    "description" : "Arquillian Container Test Implementation Base provides the base implementation for Arquillian's container test extension, wiring deployment generation, run-mode selection, protocol execution, and resource enrichment into the Arquillian test lifecycle. It supplies client and container-side controllers for starting containers, deploying archives, executing tests locally or remotely, and exposing container resources such as URLs, URIs, InitialContext, Deployer, and ContainerController.",
metadata/software.amazon.awssdk/http-auth-aws/index.json:9:    "description" : "The AWS SDK for Java HTTP Auth AWS module provides interfaces and implementations for AWS-specific HTTP authentication. It includes request-signing support for AWS Signature Version 4 and Signature Version 4A, including signer schemes and related payload and checksum handling used by AWS SDK clients.",
metadata/org.scalameta/scalafmt-sysops_2.13/index.json:9:    "description" : "Scalafmt Sysops provides the file-system, path-finding, operating-system, and Git operation utilities used by Scalafmt on the JVM. It supports Scalafmt, a Scala code formatter that keeps Scala source code layout consistent across editors, build tools, and command-line workflows.",
