metadata/org.jboss.arquillian.container/arquillian-container-test-api/index.json:48:    "description" : "Arquillian Container Test API provides annotations and helper APIs used to declare deployments, target containers, run modes, and protocols for Arquillian-managed integration tests. It lets tests coordinate container startup, deployment, and client-vs-container execution through contracts such as Deployment, RunAsClient, TargetsContainer, Deployer, and ContainerController.",
metadata/software.amazon.awssdk/secretsmanager/index.json:9:    "description" : "The AWS SDK for Java v2 Secrets Manager module provides generated clients and models for calling AWS Secrets Manager. It lets JVM applications create, retrieve, rotate, and manage secrets through the AWS Secrets Manager service.",
metadata/org.skyscreamer/jsonassert/index.json:9:    "description" : "JSONassert provides assertions for comparing expected and actual JSON documents in Java tests while supporting strict or lenient comparison modes. It reduces brittle REST/API tests by comparing JSON structure and values rather than requiring exact string equality or fixed object ordering.",
