metadata/io.ktor/ktor-io-jvm/index.json:9:    "description" : "Ktor IO provides Ktor's coroutine-friendly byte channel and packet I/O primitives for streaming data across platforms. The JVM artifact supplies the JVM implementations and integrations with Java IO/NIO, charsets, and byte-buffer pools used by Ktor clients, servers, and related libraries.",
