metadata/io.ktor/ktor-serialization-kotlinx-jvm/index.json:9:    "description" : "Ktor Serialization Kotlinx provides Ktor content converters backed by kotlinx.serialization for Kotlin applications. Its JVM artifact supplies the shared converter and WebSocket serialization support used by Ktor clients and servers to serialize and deserialize payloads with kotlinx.serialization formats.",
