metadata/org.mongodb/mongo-java-driver/index.json:9:    "description" : "MongoDB Java Driver provides Java APIs for connecting applications to MongoDB and performing database, collection, query, and write operations. The 3.9.0 uber-artifact bundles the legacy driver, mongodb-driver, mongodb-driver-core, and bson, including client APIs, protocol support, and BSON encoding and decoding.",
metadata/org.mongodb/mongo-java-driver/index.json:47:    "description" : "MongoDB Java Driver provides Java APIs for connecting applications to MongoDB and performing database, collection, query, and write operations. The 3.4.0 uber-artifact bundles mongodb-driver, mongodb-driver-core, and bson, including client APIs, protocol support, and BSON encoding and decoding.",
