metadata/org.apache.maven.resolver/maven-resolver-impl/index.json:9:    "description" : "Maven Resolver Impl provides the default implementation of Maven Artifact Resolver's repository system. It coordinates dependency collection, artifact and metadata resolution, session handling, update checks, and related services used by Maven and resolver-based tools.",
