metadata/org.mariadb/r2dbc-mariadb/index.json:12:    "description": "MariaDB Connector/R2DBC is a non-blocking Java driver that implements the R2DBC API for MariaDB and MySQL databases. It lets reactive applications create connections and execute SQL asynchronously against those databases.",
