metadata/org.apache.maven.resolver/maven-resolver-connector-basic/index.json:9:    "description" : "Maven Resolver Connector Basic provides the standard repository connector implementation for Maven Artifact Resolver repositories that use URI-based layouts. It coordinates artifact and metadata transfers through the Resolver connector SPI and configured transport implementations.",
