metadata/com.akuleshov7/ktoml-core-jvm/index.json:9:    "description" : "KToml is a Kotlin Multiplatform TOML library built on kotlinx.serialization for parsing, encoding, and decoding TOML documents. The ktoml-core-jvm artifact provides the JVM implementation of its core serializer/deserializer, AST parser, annotations, configuration, and TOML writer APIs.",
