metadata/com.chuusai/shapeless_2.13/index.json:9:    "description" : "Shapeless is a generic programming library for Scala built around type classes, dependent types, generic representations, HLists, coproducts, records, lenses, and type-level operations. It lets Scala code derive boilerplate-free, type-safe behavior over case classes and algebraic data types, supporting abstractions such as polymorphic functions, compile-time operations on products, and automatic type class derivation.",
