metadata/com.geirsson/metaconfig-typesafe-config_2.13/index.json:9:    "description" : "Metaconfig is a Scala configuration library used to define typed configuration codecs and parse configuration data for tools such as Scalafix and Scalafmt. The metaconfig-typesafe-config module integrates Metaconfig with Typesafe Config so HOCON input can be converted into Metaconfig values and decoded into Scala classes.",
