metadata/com.sun.mail/jakarta.mail/index.json:13:    "description": "Jakarta Mail provides a Java API for composing, sending, receiving, and processing email messages. It models common mail concepts and includes protocol-specific support for internet mail standards such as SMTP, POP3, IMAP, and MIME.",
metadata/dev.zio/zio-interop-tracer_3/index.json:9:    "description" : "ZIO Interop Tracer is the JVM tracing support module used by ZIO Interop Cats to derive ZIO Trace values for interop-created lambdas. It inspects lambda class and source-line metadata and caches computed traces so Cats Effect and ZIO interop code can report meaningful call sites.",
